Task 2b

trees$Girth2 <- (trees$Girth)^2
trees$Girth2Height <- trees$Girth2*trees$Height
X <- matrix(cbind(rep(1, 31), trees$Girth, trees$Height, trees$Girth2, trees$Girth2Height), 31, 5)
